    "body": "## Problem:\r\n- Currently same progress stat get's displayed on statusline of all windows. This is repeatitive and noisy.\r\n- Also for multiple running progress Progress: {N} items {percent}% format can be simplified\r\n\r\n## Solultion:\r\n- Only display progress-status on the focused window\r\n- update multi progress format to Progress: AVG%(N)\r\n\r\n[context](https://github.com/neovim/neovim/pull/35428#discussion_r2965206856)\r\ncc @justinmk ",
    "closed_at": "2026-03-24T12:28:44Z",
    "comment_data": [
