            },
            "author_association": "MEMBER",
            "body": "```suggestion\n          \"%{% luaeval('(pcall(require, ''vim.ui'') and vim.api.nvim_get_current_win() == (vim.g.actual_curwin or -1) and vim.ui.progress_status()) or '''' ')%}\",\n```",
